      "span_text": "In, it is assumed that the robot will execute a given sequence of control laws, denoted as (κ 0, τ 0 ), (κ 1, τ 1 ),., (κ N, τ N ), where τ i indicates the time when the system will switch from executing the control law κ i−1 to the control law κ i."
